    "The highest accuracy is observed on MCTest with 92.5% and the lowest on CMCQRD with 79.9%.",
    "Additionally, the performance of the model is reported on each dataset after generating 8 paraphrases for each context (see Section 4.1).",
    "It is observed there is a consistent drop in performance of the model on the paraphrased contexts compared to the original.",
    "This is expected as the nature of the machine generated paraphrased contexts do not necessarily align with the type of contexts observed in the original dataset.",
